<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Wabbajack!</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">

  <!-- Latest compiled and minified CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">

  <!-- Optional theme -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.2/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css">

  <script type="text/javascript" src="js/jquery-2.1.3.min.js"></script>

  <!-- Latest compiled and minified JavaScript -->
  <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>
      The Wabbajack!
    </h1>

    <blockquote>
      <%= yield %>
    </blockquote>

    <div class="first-half col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6">
      <p>
        New from ES Corp. comes the product we've all been waiting for.<br>
        Endless amusement is only a moment away with the new and exciting Wabbajack!<br><br>
        The best thing since sliced sweet rolls is sure to dazzle and amaze all ages.<br><br>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="second-half col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6">
      <p>
        Touch the target and let the madness unfold.<br>
        Comes with a variety of effects including but not limited to...<br><br>
        Fire, Frost, Lightning, Disintegration, Healing, Transformation, Invisibility, <br>Fear, Death, Paralysis, Decapitation, Resurrection, and Summoning.<br><br>
        Adult supervision recommended.
      </p>
    </div>
    <img src="http://img1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20120229014132/elderscrolls/images/2/24/StaffWabbajack.png" alt="" class="col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-md-4 col-lg-4 col-xs-offset-4 col-sm-offset-4 col-md-offset-4 col-lg-offset-4"/><br><br>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
